{"tid":1522040,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家起到個火魔防線就要轉埸喇","createTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:14:11.000Z","uid":38705,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7729c7fad28f5095d6a1ca206c4f5f2bb3e467c2","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"個火一熄班狗即刻到,你地就走唔切喇<br />\n寧願呢度set完去下個點再set過<br />\n唔好成班企定定望住個火自high呀"},{"pid":"5977febc9e133e8af0b46185bb89015ecad88d00","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"班狗一衝,我地又走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7768996184c9be9176d0f311d39d906144ae44f","tid":1522040,"uid":278649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"唉，唔走又等班畜黎到又驚到跑<br />\n跑又跑唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a13ca9e6c5a6fca37ea7630c479ad980fd5332","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"轉埸呀大家<br />\n聽日機埸重要你地呀<br />\n11月區議會選舉等緊你嗰一票呀"},{"pid":"803ff2ab43d6d774f0cdc9489592ce0790172a3a","tid":1522040,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5977febc9e133e8af0b46185bb89015ecad88d00","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"班狗一衝,我地又走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"好多人睇到救埋火先肯走<br />\n走果陣又要慢慢行<br />\n真係唔驚比人捉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2459347be0f5e3aa51d2087503f94d71e74838f6","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"跑得慢真係唔緊要<br />\n最緊要你知自己跑得慢<br />\n自己就盡早轉場<br />\n唔好送頭呀"},{"pid":"a06c78c5918c50e76b135cec525f35a2c4a8d62e","tid":1522040,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"$ush"},{"pid":"a7f381917bbabd61e902e27e20080b39b24ac6d2","tid":1522040,"uid":314979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wfaf2iJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfaf2iJ.gif&h=ffb1968d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ab9189596c92154e5113e3dc26fe577d6ab42e3","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"今次教訓我地<br />\n第二條防線要早啲set呀大家<br />\n唔好再以為班狗會等埋你地high完先衝"},{"pid":"0c72ca6b8251b04556fa83ec3a57b5c7b7f35674","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"一係轉場一個早啲撤<br />\n我地條路有排行呀"},{"pid":"d836e8f28ac687ed0f46c0762488fe546c688453","tid":1522040,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"縱火終生監禁嫁"},{"pid":"bed1849aed1211f7a89ad90d01e195b0d5e4e127","tid":1522040,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"仲諗住仲今日零拘捕，唉"},{"pid":"72534b549cc04ad77e54a7b712eded65eb0bc544","tid":1522040,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. hot sodium carbonate solution<br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行"},{"pid":"8e0a16f77235194aa3e98141d77cc8f7f844257a","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d836e8f28ac687ed0f46c0762488fe546c688453","tid":1522040,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"縱火終生監禁嫁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"今晚捉到嗰啲肯定係唔係都會告縱火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好咁傻豬,以為玩緊camp fire呀"},{"pid":"153c2ca127b34e7a7ef57e23a8f5b2263872ec0d","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"大家要一齊行落去呀!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"baef884ccfe6818f78a2690b69f94d041c7e91cf","tid":1522040,"uid":237809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77439ba92548c74edcb8fc4e2453329f56be473d","tid":1522040,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e0a16f77235194aa3e98141d77cc8f7f844257a","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d836e8f28ac687ed0f46c0762488fe546c688453","tid":1522040,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"縱火終生監禁嫁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"今晚捉到嗰啲肯定係唔係都會告縱火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好咁傻豬,以為玩緊camp fire呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"其實點告得入<br />\n果度咁撚多人<br />\n好難證明邊個有份縱火<br 