s/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cfdbb49ee248c701e3f84bdca4c0b48b19485f","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"有水炮車推緊重係度慢慢行<br />\n大家個心態係咪真係覺得唔會有事?"},{"pid":"f1c21fa4e98319adf25e9c891dcce2e7f3eebb2d","tid":1522040,"uid":302496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82d8faa7ee8c2eb032fbf45f42dfd3ebaf9b552","tid":1522040,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"金鐘散得切<br />\n係銅記灣仔太多人食花生<br />\n以為唔會咁快推到"},{"pid":"a659531db04a3074374b3d151c08f4fcf8055cc7","tid":1522040,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7f381917bbabd61e902e27e20080b39b24ac6d2","tid":1522040,"uid":314979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wfaf2iJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfaf2iJ.gif&h=ffb1968d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"Cls"}]}